Mora Vittum Hey guys! NHS and BSC are partnering to host a fright fest trip on October 28th from 4:30pm-10:30pm. The cost is $65 and includes bus and park entry. Anna C Hi all! General information for both options to help clear some things up. At the Drake, we‚Äôll have to pay for decorations. This will bring the total cost of tickets up to 150$ ish. At Morgan Manufacturing, we do have to pay for food and security as well as decorations. Morgan is more spacious and includes some spaces for sofas if wanted. Tickets will likely total up to around 200$ish because of this. Baseline, without any added costs, the total ticket price difference that we hope the track team will help subsidize (in addition to subsidies we are already planning for) is 16,000$.
